Context: The George Brown College offers Interior Decorating courses. Some graduates of this program have gone on to run successful decorating companies, such as Jessica Waks. The college is located on the traditional territory of the Mississaugas of the Credit First Nation and other Indigenous peoples. The information contained in the website is subject to change without notice and should not be viewed as a representation or warranty for students regarding fee requirements. It's important for students to verify George Brown College fee requirements themselves. There are student success stories available on the college website, which can be accessed through the menu or by visiting the Student Success Stories webpage.
